│ that some instructions may be\n  // legitimately excluded from the VPlan because they are loop-invariant and\n   │
│ // can be hoisted, or because they are dead in the vectorized version.\n  // The CostCtx already tracks          │
│ instructions that should be skipped in cost\n  // computation via VecValuesToIgnore and ValuesToIgnore sets.\n   │
│ \n  // Additionally, check if the instruction is loop-invariant, as such\n  // instructions can be legitimately  │
